OL,14,FMark Drakeford's wife, Clare, died     
OL,15,Fsuddenly in January aged 71. The couple
OL,16,Fhad lived together in Pontcanna,       
OL,17,FCardiff, for 30 years. He said that    
OL,18,Fwork was what kept him going as he was 
OL,19,F"unprepared for the ferocity of grief".
